      <para id="id8562670">DESIGN YOUR OWN ROWING BOAT</para>
      <list id="id1170424205159" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Next your design team must make and improve Supertoy's rowing boat.</item>
        <item>Follow the same steps as with the hats:</item>
