      <section id="id1170425523967">
        <title>To design your own boat [LO 1.4, 1.7, 1.9, 1.11]</title>
        <para id="id1170426286232">A  Our design:</para>
        <para id="id3755002"><emphasis effect="bold"> WHAT? </emphasis>…………………………………………………………………………</para>
        <para id="id1170426514842"> For <emphasis effect="bold">WHOM?</emphasis>……………………………………………………………………..</para>
        <para id="id6061996"> For <emphasis effect="bold">WHEN?</emphasis>……………………………………………………………………..</para>
        <para id="id5901316">For <emphasis effect="bold">WHERE?</emphasis>……………………………………………………………………</para>
        <para id="id1170425339044">Explain this to your friend.</para>
        <para id="id1170427365700">B Study Supertoy’s proposal (previous page) for the boat. Explain by means of a sketch the main steps you are going to follow to make the boat. Then you can start building the boat!</para>
        <para id="id6712178">You can also use your own page. (Try to make two-dimensional drawings with the teacher’s help.)</para>
      </section>
